1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:05,910
When research spans several projects, useful insights can disappear into separate files.

2
00:00:05,910 --> 00:00:10,768
The QualCanvas Research Repository provides a place to curate insight

3
00:00:10,768 --> 00:00:15,626
records across projects while the detailed analysis remains in each

4
00:00:15,626 --> 00:00:16,112
canvas.

5
00:00:16,512 --> 00:00:20,174
Open Research Repository from your authenticated workspace.

6
00:00:20,174 --> 00:00:25,406
Repository access depends on the current QualCanvas plan, so confirm

7
00:00:25,406 --> 00:00:29,592
availability before designing a team process around it.

8
00:00:29,992 --> 00:00:34,111
Choose New Repository and add a name and description.

9
00:00:34,111 --> 00:00:38,689
A durable customer journey, service area or research programme usually

10
00:00:38,689 --> 00:00:42,808
makes a better boundary than a temporary presentation deadline.

11
00:00:43,208 --> 00:00:49,181
Each canvas remains the home of transcripts, coding and project-level reasoning.

12
00:00:49,181 --> 00:00:54,611
Promote a concise insight only after reviewing its supporting evidence,

13
00:00:54,611 --> 00:00:56,240
context and limitations.

14
00:00:56,640 --> 00:01:01,016
Before adding an insight, capture the claim, the evidence behind

15
00:01:01,016 --> 00:01:05,393
it, the context in which it applies and any uncertainty

16
00:01:05,393 --> 00:01:06,706
or negative cases.

17
00:01:06,706 --> 00:01:11,520
A memorable sentence without those boundaries can become misleading when reused.

18
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:16,091
For a team repository, assign owners and review dates.

19
00:01:16,091 --> 00:01:20,727
Retire or revise an insight when later research changes the

20
00:01:20,727 --> 00:01:25,362
evidence, and maintain the same participant privacy controls used in

21
00:01:25,362 --> 00:01:26,752
the source project.

22
00:01:27,152 --> 00:01:32,703
A useful repository has a clear scope, traceable evidence, contextual

23
00:01:32,703 --> 00:01:36,034
limits, named ownership and regular review.

24
00:01:36,034 --> 00:01:41,585
Visit the QualCanvas training centre for applied-research workflows that connect

25
00:01:41,585 --> 00:01:44,360
interviews, surveys and team handoffs.
